headline: McDonald's (MCD) Q3 2025 Earnings Call Transcript
summary: In the third quarter, McDonald's delivered global comparable sales growth of more than 3.5% with growth across all segments.  In addition, for the second quarter in a row, McDonald's delivered global system-wide sales growth of more than 6% in constant currency, reflective of the increasing contribution from new unit openings.  In contrast, traffic growth among higher-income consumers remained strong, increasing nearly double digits in the quarter.
